local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["pedagogue"]={"pedagogue","['pedəgɒg]","['pɛdəɡɑɡ]","n.教师",'n.教师,教育者,学究|||=pedagog','A new teacher usually receives a great deal of help from the more experienced pedagogue.','新老师通常能从更有经验的教师那儿获得很多的帮助。','De Gaulle was a born pedagogue who used the public platform and the television screen to great effect.','戴高乐生来喜欢教育人，他充分利用了公共讲坛和电视荧屏。'}
